PN,37801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782292708
OL,3,CStatic live facial recognition cameras
OL,4,Cto be used in London's West End and
OL,5,CSoho
OL,7,FBritain's biggest police force is
OL,8,Fexpanding its use of static live
OL,9,Ffacial recognition cameras to London's
OL,10,FWest End and Soho.
OL,12,FThe devices were used during a six-
OL,13,Fmonth pilot in Croydon, south London,
OL,14,Fbetween October 2025 and May 2026
OL,15,Fwhich saw 173 people arrested
OL,16,Fincluding a woman who had been wanted
OL,17,Ffor more than 20 years.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
