OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782292708
OL,3,CStatic live facial recognition cameras
OL,4,Cto be used in London's West End and
OL,5,CSoho
OL,7,FThey are now set to be deployed in the
OL,8,FWest End and Soho by the end of the
OL,9,Fyear, and will be rolled out to other
OL,10,Fparts of the English capital next year.
OL,12,FThe static cameras are attached to
OL,13,Fstreet furniture and monitored
OL,14,Fremotely.
OL,16,FCommissioner Sir Mark Rowley said:
OL,17,F"Facial recognition is one of the most
OL,18,Frevolutionary technology advances in
OL,19,Fpolicing in recent years.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782292708
OL,3,CStatic live facial recognition cameras
OL,4,Cto be used in London's West End and
OL,5,CSoho
OL,7,F"Public confidence in this is clear `
OL,8,Faround 80% of Londoners support its
OL,9,Fuse. That backing reflects a simple
OL,10,Ftruth: it works.
OL,12,F"We have already seen the impact in
OL,13,FCroydon, where a six-month pilot
OL,14,Fdelivered over 170 arrests, a
OL,15,Freduction in crime and a significant
OL,16,Ffall in violence against women and
OL,17,Fgirls.
OL,19,F"All these results with only one false
OL,20,Falert among hundreds of thousands of
OL,21,Fpeople.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782292708
OL,3,CStatic live facial recognition cameras
OL,4,Cto be used in London's West End and
OL,5,CSoho
OL,7,F"The technology supports officers to
OL,8,Ftarget wanted criminals and registered
OL,9,Fsex offenders. Crucially it is
OL,10,Fsupporting officers ` not replacing
OL,11,Fthem.
OL,13,F"Now we're taking that capability
OL,14,Ffurther. We want to build on our
OL,15,Fsuccess by introducing this capability
OL,16,Fto the West End and Soho by December.
OL,17,FThe use of static cameras will help us
OL,18,Fcontinue cutting crime in high-
OL,19,Ffootfall areas in central London.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782292708
OL,3,CStatic live facial recognition cameras
OL,4,Cto be used in London's West End and
OL,5,CSoho
OL,7,F"We also have to be clear about the
OL,8,Fthreat we face ` criminals are not
OL,9,Fstanding still. They are quick to
OL,10,Fexploit new technology to commit
OL,11,Foffences, evade detection and target
OL,12,Fvictims at scale. Policing cannot
OL,13,Fafford to fall behind and this is
OL,14,Fanother step towards tackling that."
OL,16,FIn the Croydon pilot, the Met said
OL,17,Fmore than 470,000 people walked past
OL,18,Fthe camera, generating one false alert
OL,19,Ffor which the person was spoken to by
OL,20,Fofficers and then allowed to leave.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782292708
OL,3,CStatic live facial recognition cameras
OL,4,Cto be used in London's West End and
OL,5,CSoho
OL,7,FSince the start of 2024, the force has
OL,8,Farrested more than 2,000 people using
OL,9,Flive facial recognition cameras.
OL,11,FAkiko Hart, director at human rights
OL,12,Forganisation Liberty, said the force
OL,13,Fshould pause its use of the technology
OL,14,Funtil a legal framework is put in
OL,15,Fplace to govern its use.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782292708
OL,3,CStatic live facial recognition cameras
OL,4,Cto be used in London's West End and
OL,5,CSoho
OL,7,F"The news that the Metropolitan Police
OL,8,Fare planning to roll out live facial
OL,9,Frecognition cameras at pace across
OL,10,FLondon is very troubling and
OL,11,Frepresents a major escalation in the
OL,12,Fuse of this technology," she said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782292708
OL,3,CStatic live facial recognition cameras
OL,4,Cto be used in London's West End and
OL,5,CSoho
OL,7,F"Robust safeguards, oversight and
OL,8,Ftransparency on the use of facial
OL,9,Frecognition cameras should have been
OL,10,Fin place before they were ever
OL,11,Fintroduced to our city centres and
OL,12,Fhigh streets. To reach the level of
OL,13,Ffixed cameras across the capital
OL,14,Fbefore we even have a law in place is
OL,15,Fdeeply concerning.
OL,17,F"The Government has committed to a
OL,18,Fdedicated legal framework for facial
OL,19,Frecognition technology.
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782292708
OL,3,CStatic live facial recognition cameras
OL,4,Cto be used in London's West End and
OL,5,CSoho
OL,7,F"It is vital that this includes clear
OL,8,Fand consistent rules around how the
OL,9,Fpolice use facial recognition to
OL,10,Fensure the rights of the public are
OL,11,Fprotected at all times.
OL,13,F"Until this in place the Metropolitan
OL,14,FPolice should pause their use of the
OL,15,Ftechnology, not expand it."
